At his second coming, he will bring both to earth, but right now you have Shalom in your heart.

00:58:06.599 --> 00:58:07.340
Peace of God.

00:58:08.382 --> 00:58:09.043
Peace of God.

00:58:09.063 --> 00:58:12.148
You can have the peace of God in every conflict.

00:58:12.248 --> 00:58:14.511
No one can take the peace of God from you.

00:58:14.552 --> 00:58:17.636
It transcends all of the understanding of the world.

00:58:17.696 --> 00:58:22.284
Do you want to avoid conflict or do you want Shalom?

00:58:23.045 --> 00:58:27.432
Do you want to avoid conflict in your family or do you want the peace of God in your family?

00:58:27.452 --> 00:58:28.914
They're completely different things.

00:58:30.210 --> 00:58:34.775
Do you want to avoid conflict at your workplace or do you want the peace of God at your workplace?

00:58:34.876 --> 00:58:36.357
They are two completely different things.

00:58:39.761 --> 00:59:00.146
That peace comes from following Him closely, knowing what you're in for, praising Him knowing that as you're delivered up, regardless of what your persecution might look like, you can be absolutely confident knowing that as you delight yourself in Him, as you follow Him, as you lean not on your own understanding,

00:59:00.834 --> 00:59:01.955
He directs your path.

00:59:01.995 --> 00:59:03.337
He gives you the words to say.

00:59:03.397 --> 00:59:07.882
This is not the fine print of being a Christian.

00:59:08.643 --> 00:59:09.624
This is at the very beginning.

00:59:10.445 --> 00:59:13.909
This is like sign on the dotted line, part of being a Christian.

00:59:16.672 --> 00:59:18.314
He doesn't hide what it looks like to follow him.

00:59:19.135 --> 00:59:28.466
He tells us up front what the cost is gonna be, opposed, misunderstood, hated, but still blessed, still called blessed.

00:59:30.402 --> 00:59:34.308
I don't want the sermon for you to be a call to go look for persecution.

00:59:34.328 --> 00:59:35.850
Like a seek out persecution.

00:59:36.091 --> 00:59:37.833
Let me see how persecution can be.

00:59:39.856 --> 00:59:42.500
It's certainly not a way to earn salvation through persecution.

00:59:42.520 --> 00:59:43.642
Salvation is grace alone.

00:59:45.945 --> 00:59:46.847
But it's a recentering.

00:59:48.709 --> 00:59:50.772
It's a recentering on what you said yes to.

00:59:52.175 --> 00:59:54.077
What you're considering saying yes to.

00:59:55.640 --> 00:59:59.826
That saying yes to Jesus is saying yes to following Him.

01:00:00.354 --> 01:00:01.876
Honestly and truly.

01:00:03.838 --> 01:00:05.821
Question is not do you believe in Jesus?

01:00:05.901 --> 01:00:10.546
The question is do you understand what being a disciple of Christ looks like?

01:00:10.727 --> 01:00:11.848
And I pray that you do.

01:00:11.908 --> 01:00:19.678
And when you do, what a joy it is to say, I have decided to follow Jesus.

01:00:21.640 --> 01:00:24.944
The world behind me, the cross before me.

01:00:24.964 --> 01:00:27.007
No turning back, amen.

01:00:27.727 --> 01:00:28.669
Amen.

01:00:28.689 --> 01:00:29.810
Let's pray, Lord we thank you.

01:00:31.458 --> 01:00:32.439
God, we glorify you.

01:00:37.124 --> 01:00:40.668
Lord, to be hated by all and loved by one.

01:00:47.836 --> 01:00:48.657
Nothing else matters.

01:00:51.219 --> 01:00:52.961
I pray that encouragement upon this room.

01:00:56.005 --> 01:01:01.010
God, and the ones that don't hate us, the people that were surrounded by this church, Lord, what a beautiful thing.

01:01:01.474 --> 01:01:02.435
We thank you for that.

01:01:02.495 --> 01:01:13.727
We recognize that we are so blessed to be in a place surrounded by people that don't actually hate us because your word has transformed community.

01:01:14.928 --> 01:01:18.953
God but realizing that we are the minority of the world.

01:01:21.896 --> 01:01:27.922
People all throughout the world that death is knocking on the door.

01:01:29.442 --> 01:01:34.389
This is a promise they hold on to every single day because it's so close.

01:01:34.829 --> 01:01:37.673
Lord, pray that we would live as if that were true for us.

01:01:38.835 --> 01:01:44.803
Lord, and we have confidence that when you place us in those positions, that you're gonna give us the words to say.

01:01:47.887 --> 01:01:49.409
Lord, we thank you for your faithfulness.

01:01:50.650 --> 01:01:51.752
We thank you that you don't.

01:01:53.875 --> 01:01:56.018
You don't tell us that everything's gonna be easy.

01:01:56.739 --> 01:01:59.282
You just tell us everything you do will have a purpose.

01:01:59.874 --> 01:02:00.278
And it does.

01:02:00.863 --> 01:02:01.832
And we thank you.

01:02:01.852 --> 01:02:02.478
We glorify you.

01:02:03.043 --> 01:02:03.629
In Jesus' name.

01:02:04.275 --> 01:02:04.658
Amen.
